sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser as Browser (SPA)
    participant Django as Django Backend
    participant Cognito as AWS Cognito
    participant IdP as IdP (Entra ID)
    participant PostAuth as PostAuthFederationLink Lambda
    participant PreToken as PreTokenGeneration Lambda

    Note over Browser,PreToken: Migration - first SAML login via Cognito

    Note over Browser: Generate PKCE pair and state nonce<br/>Store in sessionStorage

    Browser->>Django: GET /api/auth/discovery
    Note over Django: Look up IdP by email domain<br/>Build Cognito authorize URL with PKCE params
    Django-->>Browser: 302 to Cognito /oauth2/authorize

    Browser->>Cognito: GET /oauth2/authorize?identity_provider=EntraSaml&...
    Cognito-->>Browser: 302 to IdP login page

    Browser->>IdP: GET (SAML AuthnRequest redirect)
    Note over IdP: User authenticates
    IdP->>Cognito: POST /oauth2/idpresponse (SAMLResponse)
    Note over Cognito: Validate assertion signature (X.509 cert)<br/>Create federated Cognito user - generate auth code
    Cognito-->>Browser: 302 to callback_url?code=AUTH_CODE&state=nonce

    Note over Browser: Verify state matches sessionStorage value

    Browser->>Cognito: POST /oauth2/token (code + code_verifier)
    Note over Cognito: Verify PKCE - trigger PostAuthentication

    Cognito->>PostAuth: PostAuthentication event
    PostAuth->>Django: GET /api/internal/user-lookup/?email=...
    Django-->>PostAuth: 200 {"id":42,"email":"user@example.com"}
    PostAuth->>Django: POST /api/internal/link-cognito/
    Django-->>PostAuth: 200 {"linked":true}
    PostAuth->>Cognito: AdminUpdateUserAttributes custom:django_id="42"

    Cognito->>PreToken: PreTokenGeneration event
    PreToken->>Django: POST /api/internal/login-access-check/
    Django-->>PreToken: 200 {"allowed":true,"django_id":"42"}
    PreToken-->>Cognito: claimsToAddOrOverride={django_id:"42"}

    Cognito-->>Browser: {id_token, access_token, refresh_token}
